Facebook OpenID Provider for EgliseInfo
=======================================

http://egliseinfo-facebook.appspot.com/

An OpenID Provider app which allows Facebook users to log into
any OpenID site using their Facebook account.

Google AppEngine Federated Login is supported too.

Based on http://openid-provider.appspot.com/ sources, ported to latest
python-openid library (included) by the project:
http://appengine-openid-provider.googlecode.com/

Uses Facebook Platform Python SDK: https://github.com/facebook/python-sdk

For more about OpenID, see:
  http://openid.net/
  http://openid.net/about.bml
